<p>Historic areas like Benson and Florence may require specialized HVAC solutions to work with older ductwork and electrical systems, but their mature tree coverage provides natural cooling benefits. Midtown neighborhoods such as Dundee and Blackstone offer excellent solar potential with their mix of architectural styles and strong community support for sustainable energy. The growing downtown and NoDo (North of Dodge) areas are seeing increased interest in energy-efficient systems as young professionals prioritize sustainability and long-term cost savings in their home investments.</p>

